Lectura de la base de datos

ICFES201502 <- read.csv2("20152.csv", skip = 5)

Distribuci√≥n de los tama√±os de grupo

require(ggplot2)
## Loading required package: ggplot2
g1 <- ggplot(ICFES201502, aes(EVALUADOS))
g1 + geom_histogram(binwidth = 10, closed = "right") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 1000, 20)) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 2500, 200)) +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1))

g1 <- ggplot(ICFES201502, aes(log10(EVALUADOS)))
g1 + geom_histogram(binwidth = 0.05, closed = "right") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 3, 0.1)) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 2500, 100)) +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1))

Distribuci√≥n de instituciones educativas por jornada

require(ggplot2)
g1 <- ggplot(ICFES201502, aes(JORNADA))
g1 + geom_bar() +
  theme(axis.text.x=element_text(angle=90,hjust=1,vjust=0.5)) +
  ylab("N√∫mero de IE") +
  ggtitle("Distribuci√≥n de n√∫mero de IE por jornada")

require(ggplot2)
evaluadoXjornada <- with(ICFES201502, tapply(EVALUADOS, JORNADA, sum))/1e3
datos <- data.frame(jornada = names(evaluadoXjornada), evaluadoXjornada = evaluadoXjornada)
g2 <- ggplot(datos, aes(jornada, evaluadoXjornada)) 
g2 + geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
     ylab("Evaluados (miles)") +
     theme(axis.text.x=element_text(angle=90,hjust=1,vjust=0.5))

require(ggplot2)
g1 <- ggplot(ICFES201502, aes(JORNADA, EVALUADOS, fill = NATURALEZA))
g1 + geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = "dodge", width = 0.5) +
     facet_grid(. ~ CALENDARIO) +
     theme(axis.text.x=element_text(angle=90,hjust=1,vjust=0.5))

ICFES201502_1 <- droplevels(subset(ICFES201502, (JORNADA %in% 
                          c("COMPLETA U ORDINARIA","MA√ëANA","TARDE")) &
                          CALENDARIO == "A"))
promPond <- with(ICFES201502_1, 
     tapply(seq(along=DEPARTAMENTO), DEPARTAMENTO, 
            function(i, x=PROMMATEMATICA, w=EVALUADOS) 
              weighted.mean(x[i], w[i])))
promPond <- sort(promPond, decreasing = TRUE)
ICFES201502_1$DEPARTAMENTO <- factor(ICFES201502_1$DEPARTAMENTO,
                                     levels = names(promPond))
promPondBD <- data.frame(promPond = promPond, DEPARTAMENTO = names(promPond))
require(ggplot2)
g1 <- ggplot(ICFES201502_1, aes(DEPARTAMENTO, PROMMATEMATICA))
g1 + geom_boxplot(varwidth = TRUE, outlier.size = 0.5) +
     theme(axis.text.x=element_text(angle=90,hjust=1,vjust=0.5)) +
     geom_point(data = promPondBD, aes(DEPARTAMENTO, promPond),
                col = "red")

require(ggplot2)
g1 <- ggplot(ICFES201502_1, aes(PROMMATEMATICA, PROMLECTURACRITICA))
g1 + geom_point(aes(col = EVALUADOS), alpha = 0.5) + 
     scale_colour_gradient(low = "blue", high = "red") +
     coord_fixed(1)
